<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>You currently hold an IR35 Protect policy with us.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Did you know that as a current Kingsbridge customer&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>you are entitled to a cheaper rate on a combined insurance policy?<br></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b><br></b>I’d love to build you a business insurance package, so you have all the business cover you need wrapped into one single neat, affordable payment.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>It only takes 5-10 minutes to provide you with a comprehensive no-obligation quote.&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Not ready for a quote yet?</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm3g-k74-js2/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>Book a call with me</b></a><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;closer to your renewal date.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively,&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">let me know your renewal date so I can contact you nearer the time</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
